import Vue from 'vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import PersonaList from '../components/PersonaList.vue'
import PersonaForm from '../components/PersonaForm.vue'

Vue.use(VueRouter)

const routes = [
  { path: '/', name: 'personas', component: PersonaList },
  { path: '/personas/create', name: 'createPersona', component: PersonaForm },
  { path: '/personas/edit/:id', name: 'editPersona', component: PersonaForm }
]

const router = new VueRouter({
  routes
})

export default router
